BlockSource: http://www.rsssf.com/tablese/ecua96.html

Ecuador 1996

*The season consists of a Torneo Apertura and a Torneo Clausura.  Both
*winners qualify for the Copa Libertadores 1997.  The champion is
*determined in a playoff between the two winners.  If one team wins
*both, it automatically wins the championship 1996.


Torneo Apertura


* 1.Nacional               22 15  5  2  42-16  50   [Quito]
* 2.Emelec                 22 14  4  4  50-19  46   [Guayaquil]
* 3.Barcelona              22 13  3  6  36-16  42   [Guayaquil]
* 4.Deportivo Quito        22  9  8  5  39-26  35   [Quito]
* 5.Deportivo Cuenca       22  9  7  6  25-20  34   [Cuenca]
* 6.Olmedo                 22  9  4  9  22-27  31   [Riobamba]
* 7.Espoli                 22  7  8  7  23-26  29   [Quito]
* 8.LDU Quito              22  7  4 11  30-32  25   [Quito]
* 9.Tecnico Universitario  22  7  4 11  25-42  25   [Ambato]
*10.Green Cross            22  6  2 14  18-41  20   [Manta]
*11.Aucas                  22  3  6 13  16-29  15   [Quito]
*12.LDU Portoviejo         22  4  3 15  21-53  15   [Portoviejo]

