1996 Championship Final
=======================

Nacional     2-1 Emelec
 [3' Augustin Delgado, 51' José Guerrero; 87' Em. Graciani]

Dec 22
Nacional     2-0 Emelec
 [24' Oswaldo dela Cruz, 89' Kleber Chala, att: 41,207]


Nacional champions of Ecuador 1996.


